sentences.chinese: 但是，他还是解开了袋子。

sentences.english: But he's also raced against a yak (in a sack) in Mongolia…
sentences.chinese: 而他也曾在蒙古套着袋子与一只犁牛赛跑。
每件东西都用两个袋子装好吗？

sentences.english: His bag was bulging with presents.
sentences.chinese: 她的袋子由于装了礼物而胀得鼓鼓的。

sentences.english: The birds pecked a hole in the sack.
sentences.chinese: 鸟儿把袋子啄出一个洞。

sentences.english: Moss collections are quite often begun using samples transplanted from the wild in a water-retaining bag.
sentences.chinese: 收集苔藓经常是由野外移植进一个装水的袋子中。

sentences.english: The Shipper and the Chief Officer are discussing the torn bags of castor seeds at the Dispatch Office.
sentences.chinese: 发货人跟大副正在调度室谈论蓖麻籽袋子破损的事。

sentences.english: A number of bags are worn out to a certain extend with contents leaking badly.
sentences.chinese: 许多袋子都有一定程度的破损且内货严重外漏。

sentences.english: Bags must be removed in the packinghouse away from the packing line.
sentences.chinese: 袋子必须包装厂中远离包装包装线的地方摘除。

sentences.english: Every dusk, mother would waddles home with a heavy sack on her back.
sentences.chinese: 每天黄昏，母亲都背着重重的袋子蹒跚而归。

sentences.english: Keep a bag of things you want to give away.
sentences.chinese: 用一个袋子来装起你想要送给别人的东西。

sentences.english: The bag is then unhooked or rolled up around the waist.
sentences.chinese: 这个袋子然后被解开或者卷起绕在腰部。

sentences.english: She oncentrated on tossing a few last possessions into a ditty bag.
sentences.chinese: 她把最后的几件个人物品塞进一个小袋子里。

sentences.english: You are expected to produce the tag when you collect your bag.
sentences.chinese: 您来拿袋子的时候要出示取物牌。

sentences.english: So the white bags, this is an image of the breast.
sentences.chinese: 所以把那些白色袋子比作乳房。
